quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  55,26,Zonse zimene zili pa dziko zidzatha
  55,27,Ndipo nkhope ya Ambuye wako mu Ufumu ndi mu Ulemerero idzakhalabe mpaka kalekale
  55,28,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,29,Zonse zimene zimakhala kumwamba ndi padziko lapansi zimapempha kwa Iye. Tsiku lililonse Iye amakhala ndi chochita
  55,30,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,31,"Ife tidzadza kwa inu, Oh inu magulu awiri"
  55,32,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,33,"oh inu gulu la Majini ndi Anthu! Ngati muli ndi mphamvu zodutsa malire a kumwamba ndi dziko lapansi, dutsani. Komatu inu simungadutse popanda chilolezo"
  55,34,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,35,Malawi a moto ndi utsi zidzaponyedwa kwa inu nonse awiri ndipo simudzatha kudziteteza nokha
  55,36,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,37,Ndi pamene thambo lidzagawanika pakati ndikukhala lofiira ngati mafuta osungunuka
  55,38,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,39,"Motero patsiku limeneli, sipadzakhala mafunso kuchokera kwa Munthu kapena Majini okhudza machimo awo"
  55,40,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana
  55,41,ochimwa adzadziwika ndi zizindikiro ndipo adzawagwira tsumba ndi pamapazi pawo
  55,42,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye
  55,43,Iyi ndi Gahena imene anthu ochimwa amati ndi bodza
  55,44,Iwo adzalowa m’kati mwake ndi m’kati mwa madzi ogaduka
  55,45,Kodi ndi zokoma ziti za Ambuye wanu zimene mudzakana